casebody.data:
BUTLER, Appellant, v. TOWNSEND et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by Annie Butler against James R. Townsend and others.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and FOLLETT, JJ.

Ira Leo Hamberger, for appellant. John A. Beall, for respondents.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
